; Tests for history.cc: bidirectional map_prices inversion
; Covers: (set_commodity for inverted price when source != sv)
; The --revalued flag triggers map_prices with bidirectionally=true.
; When the balance is in $ but prices are defined as EUR -> $,
; the bidirectional inversion path is exercised

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/02/01 EUR $1.20

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  $100
    Assets

2024/02/15 Test2
    Expenses  $50
    Assets

test reg Expenses --revalued -X EUR
24-Jan-15 Test                  Expenses                      EUR91        EUR91
24-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                    EUR-8        EUR83
24-Feb-15 Test2                 Expenses                      EUR42       EUR125
end test
